description: Laws banning the eviction of tenants in rent arrears due to the pandemic will end on 26 December.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man protection from eviction to end
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man protection from eviction to end - BBC News
maintext: He said many workers, particularly those in the retail sector, were still facing economic uncertainty due to the knock-on effect of Covid-19 on UK retail chains operating branches on the island.
